Food for thought:
=================
CAGD:
- Geometric Modelling Notes
  http://graphics.cs.ucdavis.edu/CAGDNotes/CAGD-Notes.html
- Guru's Lair Cubic Spline Library 
  http://www.tinaja.com/cubic01.html
- Graphics Gems Repository
  http://www.acm.org/tog/GraphicsGems/
- General polygon clipper library (gpc)
  http://www.cs.man.ac.uk/~amurta/software/index.html
- Geometry junkyard
  http://www.ics.uci.edu/~eppstein/junkyard/
- Magic Software (watch for the license !)
  http://www.magic-software.com/
- FAQ for comp.graphics.algorithms:
  http://www.landfield.com/faqs/graphics/algorithms-faq/
- Preprints
  http://xxx.lanl.gov/archive/cs/intro.html
- Graphics Paper
  http://www.graphicspapers.com/

Similar projects:
- Sodipodi
  http://sodipodi.sourceforge.net/
- Sketch Development Guide:
